data.title: NAMM.org
data.meta_description: NAMM, the National Association of Music Merchants (NAMM), commonly called NAMM in reference to the organization's popular NAMM trade shows, is the not-for-profit association that promotes the pleasures and benefits of making music and strengthens the $17 billion global music products industry. Our association—and our trade shows—serve as a hub for people wanting to seek out
data.text: NAMM Standards enable the electronic exchange of product information and transactions between trading partners. By adopting one common standard for system-to-system communication, businesses run smother and cut costs.
